00:27:10,395 --> 00:27:15,700
I didn't do it! I really didn't do it!

344
00:27:16,635 --> 00:27:21,239
I know I have a bad temper,
but I'm not that bad!

345
00:27:22,173 --> 00:27:24,676
I'm not that spiteful.

346
00:27:31,116 --> 00:27:33,118
This feels horrible.

347
00:27:37,055 --> 00:27:37,956
I don't care.

