438
00:39:42,012 --> 00:39:44,115
She won't believe me.

439
00:39:44,682 --> 00:39:47,485
She scared me saying if I don't
plead guilty, things will be worse.

440
00:39:48,652 --> 00:39:50,654
She is even scarier than the prosecutor.

441
00:39:55,926 --> 00:39:59,196
It's a misunderstanding.
Seong-bin has it all wrong.

442
00:39:59,964 --> 00:40:01,065
It can't be true.

