00:40:07,705 --> 00:40:08,973
YEONJU DISTRICT PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE

444
00:40:16,580 --> 00:40:18,816
Let me see.

445
00:40:20,017 --> 00:40:21,552
Let's try again.

446
00:40:21,886 --> 00:40:24,655
What does Judge Mun Chae-shik
like to hear the most?

447
00:40:24,755 --> 00:40:26,457
"Your Honor."

448
00:40:26,724 --> 00:40:30,361
-You're not the defendant, so?
-Be confident.

449
00:40:30,694 --> 00:40:33,364
But you're a defender, so?

450
00:40:33,497 --> 00:40:37,234
-Be modest in the trial.
-Yes, good.

451
00:40:38,436 --> 00:40:40,971
They can be such losers.

452
00:40:42,273 --> 00:40:43,774
Ms. Jjang!

453
00:40:47,244 --> 00:40:50,181
-Why?
-Your trial is in the afternoon.

454
00:40:50,281 --> 00:40:51,849
You have time in the morning, right?

455
00:40:52,316 --> 00:40:54,752
-Yes.
-Then come watch my trial.

456
00:40:55,052 --> 00:40:57,021
-Why?
-I'll show you.

457
00:40:57,254 --> 00:41:00,191
How powerful a lawyer can be
when he's armed with conviction.

458
00:41:03,928 --> 00:41:05,129
-Ms. Jjang...
-No.

459
00:41:06,430 --> 00:41:07,698
-I'll go in.
-Go Guan-woo!

460
00:41:07,798 --> 00:41:08,666
-Go Guan-woo!
-Good.

461
00:41:13,304 --> 00:41:14,205
COURTHOUSE

462
00:41:14,438 --> 00:41:20,678
You are currently living
with your 80-year-old mother, right?

463
00:41:21,312 --> 00:41:22,279
Yes.

464
00:41:22,613 --> 00:41:27,918
You gather paper and do public work
to pay her medical bills.

465
00:41:28,118 --> 00:41:30,554
You have tried everything.

466
00:41:30,955 --> 00:41:35,893
That's right, but I wasn't even close to
paying it all.

467
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:40,731
That's why I had no choice
but to steal the donation.

468
00:41:40,798 --> 00:41:45,236
It was because I wanted to live with
my mother.

469
00:41:45,903 --> 00:41:46,937
Objection.

